item.description:
Come join us in our continuing exploration of Advanced Energy Healing, focusing now on the fascinating details of Keylontic Science. The healing modality included in these translations is called Ka-tha-Ra which literally translates into Light-Sound-One.

Self-Help techniques are available to everyone, as well as additional levels for those wishing to become internationally certified as multi-dimensional energy healers.

To understand where we can access the highest and most powerful healing energies from, we will view a DVD explaining the multi-dimensional structure of creation.

Please do NOT park in the driveway with the "ULCS Clinic" sign. Instead go up the first driveway which has the Meetup Sign at the end.

All Meetups are subject to last minute cancellation in the event of illness of the host, so be sure to check the website before leaving.
item.name: March Advanced Energy Healing Meetup - Structure of Our Multi-Dimensional Cosmos
